metadata.name: Executive Pass
metadata.description: The 2nd Tier in the NFT Unity Ecosystem, and at a total count of 777 NFTs at $50 US or approximately .0225 Eth.  These will be used as incentives to bring and onboard Vetted and doxed teams.  This also allows for direct access to the Founders Branch of the Ecosystem and will regulate bylaws and voting on Community Standards.  As an Executive Member, you get time to Present your project, Ideas, and anything regarding Positive business-type flow.
